[{"question":"Really?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":15,"aSentId":16},{"question":"Do you?","answer":"Well, especially in this country because they usually get it wrong, say Sir Hopkins.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":21,"aSentId":22},{"question":"What was it?","answer":"Well, first of all, I looked at the script and I thought I don\u0027t want to do another weirdo, because I\u0027m not - wasn\u0027t quite sure.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":37,"aSentId":38},{"question":"Was that what grabbed you, that it had happened?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":50,"aSentId":51},{"question":"But you believe there is a devil?","answer":"Well, we had - I\u0027ll preface this by saying that, we had Father Gary Thomas, who is an exorcist.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":74,"aSentId":75},{"question":"And he was your expert on the film, was he?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":78,"aSentId":79},{"question":"So what do you think of my - my Latin?","answer":"I thought it was quite impressive, given it\u0027s now forgotten and all.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":83,"aSentId":84},{"question":"You?","answer":"Oh, yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":103,"aSentId":104},{"question":"How much of that is - is you?","answer":"It\u0027s all me.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":110,"aSentId":111},{"question":"You put that in there, didn\u0027t you?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":113,"aSentId":114},{"question":"And is that - and is that because you actually - that\u0027s really what you believe yourself?","answer":"That\u0027s what I believe in.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":115,"aSentId":116},{"question":"Do you believe in God?","answer":"Yes, I do.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":124,"aSentId":125},{"question":"You don\u0027t like absolutism, do you?","answer":"No.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":135,"aSentId":136},{"question":"You think that\u0027s dangerous?","answer":"I think it is dangerous.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":140,"aSentId":141},{"question":"You know, what do you make of that phenomenon?","answer":"Well, the safest answer I can give is I don\u0027t know.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":164,"aSentId":165},{"question":"He\u0027s done this, doesn\u0027t he?","answer":"He\u0027s done it, and he says some extraordinary things do happen, extrasensory perception things.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":177,"aSentId":178},{"question":"Would you believe this movie if you didn\u0027t pretty more (ph) believe in this?","answer":"No, I can\u0027t have a cynicism.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":183,"aSentId":184},{"question":"What changed?","answer":"Oh, something, a crisis in my life, some 35 years ago, and I was hell bent on destruction.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":188,"aSentId":189},{"question":"So it\u0027s a fact that you, in that moment, as an atheist, you decided to pray to God, did you?","answer":"OPKINS: Oh, I - I did.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":192,"aSentId":193},{"question":"I mean, can you - can you still do it, with the same sinister face?","answer":"Oh, dear God.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":242,"aSentId":243},{"question":"You want me to do it again?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":244,"aSentId":245},{"question":"Did you still get asked to do that?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":254,"aSentId":255},{"question":"In a way, it\u0027s become almost your catch phrase?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":256,"aSentId":257},{"question":"Do you actually drink - do you ever drink Chianti?","answer":"No.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":263,"aSentId":264},{"question":"Have you ever eat fava beans?","answer":"No.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":266,"aSentId":267},{"question":"It was one of the greatest terrifying characters ever, wasn\u0027t it?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":278,"aSentId":279},{"question":"It\u0027s the whole thing, isn\u0027t it?","answer":"They asked me the other day -","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":310,"aSentId":311},{"question":"Any vices?","answer":"Yes, any vices.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":322,"aSentId":323},{"question":"You don\u0027t smoke, do you?","answer":"No.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":331,"aSentId":332},{"question":"Or do you feel you\u0027ve had your great feeling of exercising (ph)?","answer":"I have had everything taken out of me.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":336,"aSentId":337},{"question":"Have you?","answer":"Oh, yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":344,"aSentId":345},{"question":"So you become more ruthless these days?","answer":"It\u0027s not ruthless.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":356,"aSentId":357},{"question":"Are you - are you at peace with yourself these days?","answer":"Yes, I am.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":369,"aSentId":370},{"question":"Do you still have that burning drive to achieve, to get the acclaim of your peer group?","answer":"OPKINS: No.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":386,"aSentId":387},{"question":"What would be the moment you\u0027d replay, right now, if you have the chance?","answer":"Ah.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":394,"aSentId":395},{"question":"At that moment when you\u0027re sitting there and you - how many times have you been nominated before that?","answer":"That\u0027s my first nomination.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":399,"aSentId":400},{"question":"What\u0027s going through your mind?","answer":"I didn\u0027t think I was going to get it.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":405,"aSentId":406},{"question":"Was that - was that the greatest rush you\u0027ve ever experienced?","answer":"Yes, it was.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":411,"aSentId":412},{"question":"Incredible actors you\u0027re up against, are you?","answer":"Oh, yes, the greatest in the world.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":414,"aSentId":415},{"question":"What - when you\u0027re standing there, because I\u0027m - I\u0027m unlikely to ever get this moment, when you\u0027re standing there, who were you thinking of?","answer":"I\u0027ve been thinking of my father, because he died 10 years previous, on that very night.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":418,"aSentId":419},{"question":"What would he have made of that minute you\u0027re there?","answer":"He probably smoked himself to death because he always smokes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":426,"aSentId":427},{"question":"Did you know that?","answer":"No.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":453,"aSentId":454},{"question":"Are you - are you perturbed (ph) by this?","answer":"No.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":455,"aSentId":456},{"question":"Who to you have been the greatest actors of all?","answer":"Past, present and -","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":464,"aSentId":465},{"question":"Is he - is he the greatest living actor?","answer":"I think he is.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":468,"aSentId":469},{"question":"What do you look for?","answer":"Oh, I think the power of somebody like Brando or De Niro or Betty Davis, you know, going back through time.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":475,"aSentId":476},{"question":"What do you mean?","answer":"They have a grasp of everything.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":484,"aSentId":485},{"question":"Who do you see of the younger crop today that have - that may have that?","answer":"DiCaprio certainly and I think I\u0027m a great fan of Matt Damon.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":488,"aSentId":489},{"question":"Are you drawn to the darker art?","answer":"No, it\u0027s not - it\u0027s not that.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":497,"aSentId":498},{"question":"Is it - where it is?","answer":"It should be - it\u0027s quite a large town.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":505,"aSentId":506},{"question":"The population of it would be what?","answer":"OPKINS: When I was born it\u0027s about 75,000, a lot smaller.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":508,"aSentId":509},{"question":"How much more time did it bring you as a good actor, do you think?","answer":"Well, I thought it was just the thing you did was just to drink and get smashed.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":518,"aSentId":519},{"question":"Do all great actors have to have some kind of demon?","answer":"I think you have to be -- yes, I think you have to have a bit of trouble in your life.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":531,"aSentId":532},{"question":"Does it give you the kind of tormented face that you need?","answer":"It gives you the drive.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":535,"aSentId":536},{"question":"Do you like -- do you like being famous now?","answer":"Yes, it\u0027s fun.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":541,"aSentId":542},{"question":"I tell you -- can I tell you a quick story?","answer":"Of course.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":547,"aSentId":548},{"question":"Which of the actresses do you really most admire?","answer":"Without a doubt, Jodie Foster.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":572,"aSentId":573},{"question":"Do you stay in touch with her?","answer":"No.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":574,"aSentId":575},{"question":"None at all?","answer":"None at all.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":579,"aSentId":580},{"question":"Really?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":589,"aSentId":590},{"question":"You didn\u0027t suddenly start doing your little Hannibal act for old time\u0027s sake?","answer":"No.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":593,"aSentId":594},{"question":"Is that true?","answer":"I just obey orders.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":601,"aSentId":602},{"question":"Have you got better at marriage as you\u0027ve got older?","answer":"I think so.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":612,"aSentId":613},{"question":"If you had your time again -- this is your third marriage, would you have played things differently in your previous marriages?","answer":"You can\u0027t go back and second guess yourself.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":621,"aSentId":622},{"question":"Why do you love America so much?","answer":"I think it was just something to do with the post-war years.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":633,"aSentId":634},{"question":"Steven Tyler and Jennifer Lopez with Randy?","answer":"They\u0027re terrific.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":659,"aSentId":660},{"question":"Do you miss a bit of that grit though?","answer":"Well, I don\u0027t know.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":666,"aSentId":667},{"question":"Isn\u0027t Randy one of your mates?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":677,"aSentId":678},{"question":"Is he your only famous friend?","answer":"He\u0027s my only famous friend.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":681,"aSentId":682},{"question":"Are you?","answer":"No.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":686,"aSentId":687},{"question":"Do you go to the Oscars?","answer":"I went about two years ago, I think.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":691,"aSentId":692},{"question":"Does it really?","answer":"I don\u0027t know what it is.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":703,"aSentId":704},{"question":"Is that one of the reasons you live out in Malibu?","answer":"Yes, as far away from --","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":706,"aSentId":707},{"question":"Is there a lot of phoniness really that does on in the business?","answer":"Well, I\u0027m not going to say that.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":710,"aSentId":711},{"question":"Do you think there\u0027s been a sort of breakdown in priorities?","answer":"Yes, I do.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":719,"aSentId":720},{"question":"If I wrote my own epitaph, it would be -- well, first of all, do you know Mel Blanc, the vocal guy?","answer":"ORGAN: Of course.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":737,"aSentId":738},{"question":"Because what we are about to see, Michelle, is your mother actually undergoing an exorcism for real, right?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":758,"aSentId":759},{"question":"Are these -- are these classic signs of somebody who has been, in your view, possessed by the devil?","answer":"Oh, absolutely.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":777,"aSentId":778},{"question":"I mean, it must have been, as a daughter, just almost unbearable to watch this, wasn\u0027t it?","answer":"It\u0027s a nightmare.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":785,"aSentId":786},{"question":"Was there a time when your mother was perfectly normal or did she always have this?","answer":"No, no, no.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":789,"aSentId":790},{"question":"Do you remember the first time it happened?","answer":"Oh, yes, I do.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":794,"aSentId":795},{"question":"How old were you?","answer":"Fifteen.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":797,"aSentId":798},{"question":"And it was a similar scene to the one we witnessed?","answer":"Yes, actually that looked like one of the first ones.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":799,"aSentId":800},{"question":"ORGAN: Do you believe that she was possessed by the devil or evil spirits?","answer":"I do.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":819,"aSentId":820},{"question":"So I guess the obvious question is, why would this happen to somebody like Patty (ph)?","answer":"Pat Reading was an exception.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":829,"aSentId":830},{"question":"-- and she had 16 of these incidents where you had to bring a priest in, right?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":844,"aSentId":845},{"question":"When she came around, did she have any memory of what had happened?","answer":"No memory at all.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":846,"aSentId":847},{"question":"Were you honest with her?","answer":"In the beginning, I didn\u0027t want to tell her everything.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":852,"aSentId":853},{"question":"Did you show her the video?","answer":"I don\u0027t believe that one, no.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":856,"aSentId":857},{"question":"I mean, so for people who are watching this who may have a similar situation going on in their homes, how should they deal with this?","answer":"Basically, rule everything out from a medical perspective, a psychological perspective.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":860,"aSentId":861},{"question":"Do you believe that they\u0027re linked in some way?","answer":"She had what they believe was pancreatic cancer or colon cancer.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":870,"aSentId":871},{"question":"I mean, why should people bother, John, in having these if they\u0027re not going to work?","answer":"Well, the key factor with this is very seldomly (ph) an exorcism or a deliverance is very successful on one try.","docId":"110205pmt","qSentId":881,"aSentId":882}]